# Deploy Workflow

After packaging a new version (`npm run dist`), always extract the zip to the local EverQuest directory so the user runs the latest build:

```powershell
if (Test-Path "z:\Everquest P99\p99-meter") { Remove-Item "z:\Everquest P99\p99-meter" -Recurse -Force }
Expand-Archive -Path "z:\Everquest P99\AddOns\p99-meter\out\p99-meter-v<VERSION>.zip" -DestinationPath "z:\Everquest P99\" -Force
```

Do this automatically whenever you package and push a release — don't wait to be asked.
